# Michael Kühn – Frontend Portfolio

Modern frontend portfolio built with HTML, CSS and JavaScript.

## Features

- Responsive layout
- Animated overlay navigation
- Multi-language support (EN / DE)
- Interactive project section
- Mobile viewport hover system
- Legal notice and privacy pages
- Clean minimal UI

## Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Responsive Design
- i18n system

## Projects

- Join
- El Pollo Loco
- Pokédex
- Order App

